{"tid":2169812,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【逃走他鄉】英國15大宜居地區 英格蘭東部罪案率低＋快樂指數高","createTime":"2020-08-22T19:12:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-23T23:28:18.000Z","uid":79563,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"75fdda9854d3647625a491ec506f4b0eaac9f34d","tid":2169812,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T19:12:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20200730/EG6WRNTMIVAXLNMJKXX7WB6HTQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20200730%2FEG6WRNTMIVAXLNMJKXX7WB6HTQ%2F&d=aFiO92UEzPWfS5u3FViI6a7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=7b099051\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20200730%2FEG6WRNTMIVAXLNMJKXX7WB6HTQ%2F&h=f8a8bf6e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20200730/EG6WRNTMIVAXLNMJKXX7WB6HTQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n英國面積比香港大220倍，全國分為近百個郡、數百個地區，到底哪一個地方最適合你和家人？筆者曾在英國留學，現居劍橋，任職英國寄宿學校廚師及小食檔老闆。在此分享一下，筆者在15個英國地區的生活見聞和一手資訊，排名不分先後。<br />\n<br />\n1.倫敦 London<br />\n<br />\n倫敦生活指數全國最貴，跟香港相似，房價最高，單身人士的share house共住模式相當流行，工作機會最多。筆者在倫敦工作時，繁忙時間塞車問題嚴重，主要以地鐵代步，平均每日交通費約50至100港元，惟地鐵亦常有延誤或維修。娛樂選擇較多，適合怕悶的港人：蘇豪區、音樂會、露天戲院、嘉年華、唐人街、市集商場，甚至有卡拉OK。<br />\n<br />\n2. 曼徹斯特 Manchester<br />\n<br />\n曼徹斯特的市區總人口在英國排名第二，僅次於倫敦。作為曼聯和曼城主場，又鄰近利物浦，就業機會不輸倫敦，惟人工略低一點，開支也相對較低。她是最多華人和中國留學生的英國城市之一。英國有唐人街的城市包括：倫敦、利物浦、伯明翰、紐卡素和曼徹斯特。"},{"pid":"e6cf01ef61da939e65bba6565abac25ae8b91bd7","tid":2169812,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T19:14:17.000Z","msg":"3. 伯明翰 Birmingham<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/uY6ykPqOp7QepPmhKgbrsfiYh8M=/802x601/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RUTJB37VSVASDAAXQD5HYPH33M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FuY6ykPqOp7QepPmhKgbrsfiYh8M%3D%2F802x601%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRUTJB37VSVASDAAXQD5HYPH33M.jpg&h=ea432de5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n伯明翰一年一度的德國聖誕市集，吸引大量遊客。自工業革命以來，伯明翰是英國大型工業城市，運河比威尼斯還要長，跟曼徹斯特齊名英國第二大城市，工作機會多。<br />\n<br />\n4. 愛丁堡 Edinburgh<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/roWHJ2UzET7ndsbXn74bCyvp8-U=/802x534/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/27DI6E556VBHTKUP4CKRMCQSXU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FroWHJ2UzET7ndsbXn74bCyvp8-U%3D%2F802x534%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F27DI6E556VBHTKUP4CKRMCQSXU.jpg&h=74c8b7de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n蘇格蘭首都，亦是《哈利波特》的發源地。生活指數比倫敦便宜約三成，氣溫平均比倫敦低2至3度。每年8月舉行的愛丁堡國際藝穗節是世界盃和奧運會以外的國際盛事，創造大量工作機會。前首相貝理雅的母校費蒂斯公學（Fettes College）亦位於此，被譽為是「蘇格蘭的伊頓公學 」。<br />\n<br />\n5. 卡迪夫 Cardiff<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/DhhFbY4hK_haY34lVq0NRWBmJTw=/802x601/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XUXSQ6VXDFGQFMPLCINCM6MNIA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FDhhFbY4hK_haY34lVq0NRWBmJTw%3D%2F802x601%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXUXSQ6VXDFGQFMPLCINCM6MNIA.jpg&h=fdc191ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n威爾斯首都，距離倫敦約3小時車程，比倫敦細10倍。筆者在卡迪夫修讀碩士課程，市內沒有地鐵，出入以步行為主。市內商店應有盡有，生活節奏慢，有大量綠色休憩空間，卡迪夫灣、城堡、酒吧為主要娛樂。當地人口主要為退休人士和留學生，工作機會方面，護士、社工和焊接技工在當地需求較大。"},{"pid":"5b8450d7e8ee8c1feefebf9fdd0e4f0b79e7d151","tid":2169812,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T19:15:50.000Z","msg":"6. 布萊頓 Brighton<br />\n<br />\n在英國，同性婚姻是合法的。布萊頓又稱為LGBT首都，估計約十分一人口為LGBT。街頭壁畫、商店餐廳也七彩繽紛。布萊頓公學的高考成績亦多年位列全國五甲。布萊頓面向英倫海峽，市民平日最愛放工去海邊走廊散步，而當地一間餐廳Burger Brothers，亦曾獲2016年度全英國漢堡包冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n7. 約克 York<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/eWqbkEMv3tUZlBrCA3wqBf8XvK4=/802x534/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/J65EXU7ZVBEODIQSSKIXC4CKHQ.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FeWqbkEMv3tUZlBrCA3wqBf8XvK4%3D%2F802x534%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJ65EXU7ZVBEODIQSSKIXC4CKHQ.JPG&h=ca91a526&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n約克是倫敦和愛丁堡的中間點，兩小時火車可到達兩大首都。約克城牆和羅馬帝國的遺蹟吸引遊客，帶旺餐飲和零售業，亦特別多中學教師空缺。2020年首11個英國宜居地區裏，約克郡佔3個席位，分別是Selby、Hambleton和Ryedale，市中心則排第48位。<br />\n<br />\n8. 牛津 Oxford<br />\n<br />\n牛津充滿學術氣息，不止是牛津大學，牛津的中小學也很出眾。英國寄宿女校海丁頓學校（Headington School）高考成績卓越，是著名女演員Emma Watson的母校；另一間男女校Wheatley Park School則是前首相文翠珊的母校，二人均考進牛津大學。<br />\n<br />\n9. 劍橋 Cambridge<br />\n<br />\n劍橋大學和康河為當地帶來蓬勃的旅遊業，零售、餐飲等服務業工作機會多。但受武漢肺炎波及，劍橋大學宣布下學年改由網上授課，預計將打擊當地經濟。<br />\n<br />\n10. 雷丁 Reading<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/52Vn9AGOks-cDgBv6zgkukvo0wk=/802x601/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UWMECF2AK5EFDFJF5VMAUC7WPU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F52Vn9AGOks-cDgBv6zgkukvo0wk%3D%2F802x601%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUWMECF2AK5EFDFJF5VMAUC7WPU.jpg&h=c61989d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n距離英女皇「屋企」溫莎城堡和「首相工廠」伊頓公學半小時車程。歷來20位英國首相，包括約翰遜也在伊頓公學畢業。雷丁位於「英格蘭矽谷」之稱的泰晤士谷，亦是微軟和甲骨文的英國總部所在地。要注意雷丁的英文讀音，讀作 /ˈrɛdɪŋ/，跟英文字「閲讀」讀音不同。"},{"pid":"d85702fee30d4ec1fb3d941f0a63f4e115571528","tid":2169812,"uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T19:18:02.000Z","msg":"11. 布里斯托 Bristol<br />\n<br />\n布里斯托是極具活力的城市，被譽為「英國麻省理工」的英國十強老牌大學布里斯托大學居功不少。布里斯托生活指數全國第五，比曼徹斯特、雷丁、愛丁堡、約克貴，但比倫敦、牛津、布萊頓便宜。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n12. 諾域治 Norwich<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/3MiLcJZr6J3LewzHjY6IAUjdFEQ=/802x601/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/REUCV5ZXHVEGZJQIX4PAKFXQSE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F3MiLcJZr6J3LewzHjY6IAUjdFEQ%3D%2F802x601%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FREUCV5ZXHVEGZJQIX4PAKFXQSE.jpg&h=f3e8551f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英格蘭東部是英國罪案率最低的地區之一，人民健康狀況良好。距離倫敦約2小時火車。面積跟九龍相約，但人口少廿倍。諾域治市集是英國最古老的市集之一，超過200個露天攤檔，裏面一家叫Lucy&rsquo;s的炸魚薯條，長期排長龍。<br />\n<br />\n13. 斯旺西 Swansea<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ta0gIyBoZSljPk3NFVhgJ4YTFYg=/802x534/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FODS2NMB3JFFXBIYGRH7WVEWNE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fta0gIyBoZSljPk3NFVhgJ4YTFYg%3D%2F802x534%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFODS2NMB3JFFXBIYGRH7WVEWNE.jpg&h=eb8e91c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n威爾斯第二大城市，距離倫敦300多公里，相當於由台北駕車去高雄。斯旺西意譯為「天鵝海」，面向布里斯托灣畔，恬靜平和，生活指數全國排第21位，比倫敦低近四成，吸引退休人士居住，人口接近全部白人。<br />\n<br />\n14. 伊利 Ely<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/603aF_8Wog_PhIWFOkEFn-_h1yg=/802x653/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KKOT6KYVYVAB7BNW4JTQ27XCEA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F603aF_8Wog_PhIWFOkEFn-_h1yg%3D%2F802x653%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKKOT6KYVYVAB7BNW4JTQ27XCEA.jpg&h=75b9baa2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n伊利是英國最小的城市之一，乘火車前往劍橋市中心約15分鐘。城內麻雀雖小，五臟俱全，人情味濃。伊利有一間千年歷史的英國傳統寄宿學校（King&rsquo;s Ely）和大教堂，周末吸引周邊小鎮市民前往。不少英國船屋家庭停泊在市內河畔居住。<br />\n<br />\n15. 赫特福德郡 East Hertfordshire<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/tvz5pNCl0f8T2hSZovdCe_P3R1U=/802x534/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2NZ66O452RCPFOKPDS3KUJMRF4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Ftvz5pNCl0f8T2hSZovdCe_P3R1U%3D%2F802x534%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2NZ66O452RCPFOKPDS3KUJMRF4.jpg&h=b49e8490&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據Halifax 2020年《英國生活質素調查》報告，英格蘭東部的赫特福德郡是英國最宜居城市冠軍。報告指出赫特福德郡市民的快樂指數和壽命最高。<br />\n<br />\n總括而言，英國人在居住方面，最注重安全、綠色環境、負擔能力等。英格蘭東部和東南部是英國人認為最宜居的地區。"},{"pid":"652f30e2c90c3ba726e9e117110462742ed752b2","tid":2169812,"uid":352851,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T19:19:04.000Z","msg":"連登仔最啱去brighton<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6adbb2c88743e77439df0cc362f7568761fc515","tid":2169812,"uid":34899,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T19:32:34.000Z","msg":"最有英倫味係LIVERPOOL"},{"pid":"1d32a6066a200977a074e5b0443b8194160f300e","tid":2169812,"uid":81273,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T19:38:40.000Z","msg":"16. 香港 Hong Kong"},{"pid":"8bb45913d54e252cc94cb2e61583dd5ebc3acb74","tid":2169812,"uid":52594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T21:09:14.000Z","msg":"British Virgin Islands<br />\nGibratlar 去唔去得"},{"pid":"a571a184282718f2a0e9cb68c5a23f56651fc1f8","tid":2169812,"uid":226790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T17:40:48.000Z","msg":"LUTON?"},{"pid":"ab3fad08d26d073865502a483c1244f4b102cdc4","tid":2169812,"uid":221208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T18:35:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"568cca4f3af3b5653d562b1c16b4e2ea6761e7a9","tid":2169812,"uid":277816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T18:48:24.000Z","msg":"頂！無諾定咸嘅？"},{"pid":"7a52aa3d894bcdf284686c1edd97ce081ce3eac8","tid":2169812,"uid":36162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T18:49:06.000Z","msg":"sussex 如何 ?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa5a36a107cee936c97ac60234a074a4ed64301d","tid":2169812,"uid":19093,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"652f30e2c90c3ba726e9e117110462742ed752b2","tid":2169812,"uid":352851,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T19:19:04.000Z","msg":"連登仔最啱去brighton<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T18:55:22.000Z","msg":"以前成日見d 老野鳩fing fing<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4422a5a9813eed7e2e6df56f3583ae580610c35e","tid":2169812,"uid":59753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T19:25:58.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"d923634b7cf1d0033d5495d0ae70fe7330b36115","tid":2169812,"uid":59753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T19:26:47.000Z","msg":"以前聽過東北d歧視最嚴重係咪真"},{"pid":"a8e37a34f13a4e2f2c35a5cd9363b432eb59fb32","tid":2169812,"uid":143343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T19:33:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6ec41cda8b4b38812b47f514f5dc02607dd16401","tid":2169812,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T21:03:32.000Z","msg":"同力架數量有冇關？"},{"pid":"cbf6704d97192094239d73717b0507fab9505797","tid":2169812,"uid":61604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa5a36a107cee936c97ac60234a074a4ed64301d","tid":2169812,"uid":19093,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"652f30e2c90c3ba726e9e117110462742ed752b2","tid":2169812,"uid":352851,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T19:19:04.000Z","msg":"連登仔最啱去brighton<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T18:55:22.000Z","msg":"以前成日見d 老野鳩fing fing<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T21:07:18.000Z","msg":"Brighton 係英國對海地方<br />\n好正"},{"pid":"fed85c810fc2d1bb8d8b2b313a269cc20f1cf2f5","tid":2169812,"uid":61604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8e37a34f13a4e2f2c35a5cd9363b432eb59fb32","tid":2169812,"uid":143343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T19:33:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T21:07:29.000Z","msg":"凍到pk"},{"pid":"73317d2d57bd5021ebdd265da1a2b0a2c0ca70d1","tid":2169812,"uid":204106,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"652f30e2c90c3ba726e9e117110462742ed752b2","tid":2169812,"uid":352851,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T19:19:04.000Z","msg":"連登仔最啱去brighton<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T21:08:22.000Z","msg":"唔計做gay佬 日日去睇海都好舒服<br />\n掛住個到了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f77bc9d8771517753a73c521fac99ab5fa2fcdf","tid":2169812,"uid":357612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75fdda9854d3647625a491ec506f4b0eaac9f34d","tid":2169812,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T19:12:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20200730/EG6WRNTMIVAXLNMJKXX7WB6HTQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20200730%2FEG6WRNTMIVAXLNMJKXX7WB6HTQ%2F&d=aFiO92UEzPWfS5u3FViI6a7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=7b099051\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20200730%2FEG6WRNTMIVAXLNMJKXX7WB6HTQ%2F&h=f8a8bf6e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20200730/EG6WRNTMIVAXLNMJKXX7WB6HTQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n英國面積比香港大220倍，全國分為近百個郡、數百個地區，到底哪一個地方最適合你和家人？筆者曾在英國留學，現居劍橋，任職英國寄宿學校廚師及小食檔老闆。在此分享一下，筆者在15個英國地區的生活見聞和一手資訊，排名不分先後。<br />\n<br />\n1.倫敦 London<br />\n<br />\n倫敦生活指數全國最貴，跟香港相似，房價最高，單身人士的share house共住模式相當流行，工作機會最多。筆者在倫敦工作時，繁忙時間塞車問題嚴重，主要以地鐵代步，平均每日交通費約50至100港元，惟地鐵亦常有延誤或維修。娛樂選擇較多，適合怕悶的港人：蘇豪區、音樂會、露天戲院、嘉年華、唐人街、市集商場，甚至有卡拉OK。<br />\n<br />\n2. 曼徹斯特 Manchester<br />\n<br />\n曼徹斯特的市區總人口在英國排名第二，僅次於倫敦。作為曼聯和曼城主場，又鄰近利物浦，就業機會不輸倫敦，惟人工略低一點，開支也相對較低。她是最多華人和中國留學生的英國城市之一。英國有唐人街的城市包括：倫敦、利物浦、伯明翰、紐卡素和曼徹斯特。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T21:10:45.000Z","msg":"Birmingham ?! Is it a joke?!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f5bf8b3c0caaafaf5b7368925605cae3cf95f51","tid":2169812,"uid":85461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T21:16:54.000Z","msg":"香港人個個都會去魚拉突<br />\n同市光榮"},{"pid":"93c023486e9d2f8ca35addada8dce82aca89251b","tid":2169812,"uid":27251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8bb45913d54e252cc94cb2e61583dd5ebc3acb74","tid":2169812,"uid":52594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T21:09:14.000Z","msg":"British Virgin Islands<br />\nGibratlar 去唔去得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T21:29:37.000Z","msg":"直布羅陀好撚細，退休就啱"},{"pid":"355b289e5137d0d68ef422bd3662a2aeb1264ae5","tid":2169812,"uid":19012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T22:16:48.000Z","msg":"York 都講得出...真係想人地買水浸樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n重勁過支那威尼斯"},{"pid":"6b0be4213e4f037817c8e811b9279df93530a921","tid":2169812,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T22:18:30.000Z","msg":"斯旺西⋯？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}